Ignoring Certificate Errors (for self-signed certs)=ffuf -w <wordlist>:FUZZ -u "<target_host>/FUZZ" -k
Proxying Requests (via Burp Suite or other proxy)=ffuf -w <wordlist>:FUZZ -u "<target_host>/FUZZ" -x <proxy_host>:<proxy_port>
Delay Between Requests (to avoid detection)=ffuf -w <wordlist>:FUZZ -u "<target_host>/FUZZ" -p 0.1
Verbose Output (show more details)=ffuf -w <wordlist>:FUZZ -u "<target_host>/FUZZ" -v